# Development Notes

Commands
- Dev: `bun run dev` or `npm run dev` (uses `next dev --turbopack`)
- Build: `bun run build` / `npm run build`
- Start: `bun run start` / `npm run start` (serve build)
- Lint: `bun run lint` / `npm run lint`

Fonts
- Inter via `next/font/google` in `app/layout.tsx` exposed as `--font-sans`

Adding UI
- Prefer creating components under `components/ui/*` following existing `cva` variant pattern
- Use `cn` from `lib/utils` to merge classes

Styling
- Tailwind v4 tokens in `app/globals.css`; add new tokens as CSS vars
- Use `bg-…`, `text-…`, and semantic tokens (`primary`, `accent`, etc.)

Assets
- Place images in `public/images/`; import via `next/image` for optimization

Notes
- `next.config.ts` is minimal; no custom routing or images domains configured yet
- No API routes or server actions present; purely static UI today
